metadata.name: Dapper Yellow
metadata.description:
The colour yellow has been a very significant colour in history. It has been associated with good health, wealth, gods and the elites. This artwork uses yellow to accentuate the stand-out features of a dapperly dressed man. Signalling a sense of royalty with the way he dresses as well as with the way he positions his head. The closed eyes with a subtle smile is to suggest self pride as well as calmness. 

Year: 2022
Size: 3000 x 3000 pixels 
Format: PNG
